1
00:00:06,125 --> 00:00:07,664
Hi. My name's Wendy.
嗨, 我是Wendy.

2
00:00:07,665 --> 00:00:09,324
Can I get you something to drink?
我可以给你们拿点喝的吗?

3
00:00:09,325 --> 00:00:11,601
We need a bottle of mineral water
我们需要一瓶矿泉水

4
00:00:11,602 --> 00:00:14,152
and a carafe of the house red wine.
和一大瓶(carafe)自制红葡萄酒

5
00:00:16,479 --> 00:00:19,042
Sorry. Are you ready to order?
抱歉. 你们准备好点菜了吗?

6
00:00:19,043 --> 00:00:20,492
Yes, I think so.
是的, 我想是的.

7
00:00:20,493 --> 00:00:22,368
Would you like an appetizer?
你们想要一个开胃菜吗?

8
00:00:23,215 --> 00:00:26,001
Yes. What was the starter, Richard?
是的. (刚才看到的)那个开胃菜是什么, Richard?

9
00:00:26,002 --> 00:00:28,549
Yes. We'd like one spare ribs to share, please.
是的. 我们要一份排骨分着吃, 请.

10
00:00:28,550 --> 00:00:31,220
Fine. And for your main course?
好的. 对于你们的主菜呢?

11
00:00:31,221 --> 00:00:32,420
Yes. I'd like the roast chicken
是的. 我要点烤鸡

12
00:00:32,421 --> 00:00:34,641
with roast potatoes and vegetables.
带上烤土豆和蔬菜.

13
00:00:35,601 --> 00:00:37,052
Excuse me!
抱歉

14
00:00:37, 597 --> 00:00:38, 819
No problem.
没关系

15
00:00:38, 820 --> 00:00:40, 153
And for you?
你呢?

16
00:00:40, 450 --> 00:00:42, 574
I'd like the soup and salad.
我要点汤和沙拉.

17
00:00:42, 575 --> 00:00:43, 853
What kind of soup?
哪一种汤?

18
00:00:43, 854 --> 00:00:45, 933
Tomato soup, please.
西红柿汤, 请.

19
00:00:46, 871 --> 00:00:49, 361
Oh, now I'm doing it.
Oh, 现在我也在做了(打哈欠).

20
00:00:49, 505 --> 00:00:52, 312
I'm sorry. I was up all night.
不好意思. 我一宿没睡昨晚.

21
00:00:52, 313 --> 00:00:53, 825
My dog was sick.
我的狗狗生病了.

22
00:00:53, 826 --> 00:00:57, 653
Oh. How sad.
Oh. 多令人伤心.

23
00:00:57, 731 --> 00:01:00, 829
He's better today. But I'm exhausted.
他今天好多了. 但是我累坏了.

24
00:01:00, 830 --> 00:01:02, 181
Aren't we all!
我们难道不都是嘛!

